basic structure of html
doctype---it will tell the type of document and version of the html
html ---root element
head---title , external links and meta 
body-- content of the page

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>my day 1</title>
</head>
<body>
<h1>content</h1>
</body>
</html>







